#. type: Table
#: _generated-doc/main/config/quarkus-spiffe-client.adoc
msgid ""
"[[quarkus-spiffe-client_quarkus-spiffe-client-endpoint-socket]] [.property-path]##link:#quarkus-spiffe-client_quarkus-spiffe-client-endpoint-socket[`+++quarkus.spiffe-client.endpoint-socket+++`]##\n"
"config_property_copy_button:+++quarkus.spiffe-client.endpoint-socket+++[]\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"[.description]\n"
"--\n"
"SPIFFE Workload Endpoint socket URI. Supports `unix://` for Unix Domain Socket and `tcp://` for TCP transport as defined by the link:https://github.com/spiffe/spiffe/blob/main/standards/SPIFFE_Workload_Endpoint.md[SPIFFE Workload Endpoint] specification.\n"
"\n"
"If not set, the standard `SPIFFE_ENDPOINT_SOCKET` environment variable is used as a fallback, as defined by the link:https://spiffe.io/docs/latest/spiffe-specs/spiffe_workload_endpoint/#4-locating-the-endpoint[SPIFFE Workload Endpoint §4 – Locating the Endpoint] specification.\n"
"\n"
"Example values: `unix:///run/spire/sockets/agent.sock`, `tcp://127.0.0.1:8080`\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Environment variable: env_var_with_copy_button:+++QUARKUS_SPIFFE_CLIENT_ENDPOINT_SOCKET+++[]\n"
"--"
msgstr ""

#. type: Table
#: _generated-doc/main/config/quarkus-spiffe-client.adoc
